2005-08-08  Carl Worth  <cworth@cworth.org>

	* rsvg-cairo-draw.c: (_set_source_rsvg_linear_gradient),
	(_set_source_rsvg_radial_gradient): Invert matrix since cairo's
	pattern matrix is from user space to pattern space.

