	* rsvg.c (rsvg_start_svg): Fix for zoom calculations
	(rsvg_start_element): hack for Illustrator 9
	(rsvg_stop_handler_end): ditto

	* test-display.c (*): major updates. now gets built. useful utility
	* Makefile.am: ditto
	
