	* configure.in: Bump required libart version to the one
	with art_render_mask.

2002-01-04  Darin Adler  <darin@bentspoon.com>

	* configure.in: Bump version, update dependencies.
	* librsvg-2.0.pc.in: Update dependencies.

	* rsvg-bpath-util.c:
	* rsvg-css.c:
	* rsvg-css.h:
	* rsvg-defs.c:
