	* rsvg-paint-server.c: (rsvg_paint_server_parse):
	* rsvg.c: (rsvg_parse_transform), (rsvg_text_handler_characters):
	Get rid of all includes of <ctype.h> and use non-locale-specific
	g_ascii_* calls from glib instead.

